      <title>Nvidia GTC 预览：‘AI Woodstock’ 的看点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-18/nvidia-gtc-preview-what-to-watch-for-at-ai-woodstock-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nvidia 公司的年度人工智能大会“Nvidia GTC”将于周一开幕，首席执行官黄仁勋将在开幕当天发表讲话。黄通常以介绍新产品和概述他对技术发展方向的最新愿景来拉开活动序幕。彭博市场今日的 Sofia Horta e Costa 和 Bloomberg Intelligence 的 Matthew Bloxham 进行了预览。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-18/nvidia-gtc-preview-what-to-watch-for-at-ai-woodstock-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 09:40:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
