    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利表示，印度无法与中国过去 8-10% 的增长率相媲美</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/india-can-t-match-china-s-past-8-10-growth-morgan-stanley-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利首席亚洲经济学家表示，从长远来看，印度不太可能实现中国那样的8%-10%的经济增长率，尽管该投行仍然对这个南亚国家的前景持乐观态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/india-can-t-match-china-s-past-8-10-growth-morgan-stanley-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 08:32:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲天然气延续涨势，关注全球能源供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/european-gas-extends-rally-with-focus-on-global-energy-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商关注全球能源供应的脆弱性，欧洲天然气价格连续第四天上涨，这是自 1 月底以来最长的涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/european-gas-extends-rally-with-focus-on-global-energy-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 08:28:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
